          <p>Gentle walks and leash training for young pups learning proper walking behavior.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="service-card">
          <h3>Senior Dog Care</h3>
          <p>Slow-paced, gentle walks tailored to older dogs with mobility considerations.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="service-card">
          <h3>Large Breed Walking</h3>
          <p>Experienced handling for big dogs who need confident, professional walkers.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

