        </div>
        <div class="why-item">
          <h3>✓ Photo Updates</h3>
          <p>Receive photos and updates after each walk so you know your pup is happy.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="why-item">
          <h3>✓ GPS Tracking</h3>
          <p>Follow along in real-time and see exactly where your dog walked.</p>
        </div>
